Toxic Comment Classification - Usage

The pml.sif and the output_folder must be obtained from https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1bn9pdTxk2Ni_SX4jSMwuC5oHJwEyrIGT?usp=sharing since they are too large for GitHub. They have to be stored in the main directory. 

To run program, use: sbatch run.sbatch
To run program in apptainer, use: ./run.sh
If explain-mode is required, change command paramater in run.sh to "explain, if training-mode is required, use "train" in the format: python main.py <train>/<explain>"

Output files and input files are saved in ./output_folder 
